description: A new operator for Flybe Isle of Man routes could be "announced next week", the chief minister says.
title: Flybe collapse: Update on Isle of Man flights to UK due 'next week'
title_page: Flybe collapse: Update on Isle of Man flights to UK due 'next week' - BBC News
maintext: He said: "I think it would be unrealistic to have a 100% normal service in the current climate. But we would look to have the same level of service going forward."
